WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:07.800 --> 00:00:10.240
 This is the well of the sun 

00:00:12.900 --> 00:00:16.040
 a sacred source of unparalleled power 

00:00:16.580 --> 00:00:19.780
 It fills our body 

00:00:20.400 --> 00:00:23.340
 In its warmth, we are moving towards prosperity 

00:00:24.800 --> 00:00:27.680
 Until the shadow of death covers us 

00:01:06.380 --> 00:01:08.960
 Only after the destruction of the Sunwell 

00:01:09.220 --> 00:01:13.240
 We only know how much we rely on him. 

00:01:13.380 --> 00:01:15.660
 How hungry we are 

00:01:16.354 --> 00:01:18.354
 After all suffering 

00:01:18.520 --> 00:01:21.540
 I call my compatriot "Xin Duo Lei" 

00:01:21.860 --> 00:01:23.260
 Blood elf 

00:01:23.840 --> 00:01:26.360
 My compatriots asked me for answers. 

00:01:26.520 --> 00:01:29.020
 So I promised to cure them. 

00:01:29.020 --> 00:01:33.500
 I am desperately searching for the word of salvation, and Illidan gave us hope. 

00:01:35.880 --> 00:01:39.240
 Yili Dan provides a new source of strength 

00:01:39.640 --> 00:01:41.920
 So I joined him in the foreign domain. 

00:01:42.040 --> 00:01:45.700
 Swear to come back one day and lead my compatriots back to glory 

00:01:52.080 --> 00:01:54.620
 But Illidan only considers his own future. 

00:01:55.140 --> 00:01:56.620
 I started to lose patience 

00:01:57.600 --> 00:02:02.020
 Secret, I began to do my best to capture energy. 

00:02:02.780 --> 00:02:06.880
 I have experienced what is real power. 

00:02:22.340 --> 00:02:24.600
 Before it was taken away 

00:02:26.780 --> 00:02:29.080
 But all this has not been lost 

00:02:29.813 --> 00:02:31.813
 The essence of the Sunwell has escaped 

00:02:32.280 --> 00:02:35.000
 Hidden by those who think they protect it 

00:02:37.360 --> 00:02:39.360
 I have returned now 

00:02:39.360 --> 00:02:43.740
 Understand that if you want to regain the rights granted to us by God 

00:02:43.740 --> 00:02:45.440
 Sacrifice is inevitable 

00:02:46.960 --> 00:02:49.680
 So I formed a new alliance. 

00:02:50.900 --> 00:02:55.400
 The sacred radiance of the Sunwell will soon shine again 

00:02:56.520 --> 00:02:59.260
 And greet him and enter the world 

00:02:59.500 --> 00:03:03.720
 The one who can give us everything... 

00:03:10.100 --> 00:03:14.200
 Revenge Fury, Sun Well 

